About Our Restaurant
Our Story
Waterfront dining featuring local farm to table foods; Central Florida Cuisine, local craft beers, wines, and second mile hospitality. Signature dishes include Blackened Grouper Reuben, Hand-Dipped Coconut Shrimp, Florida Grass-Fed Burgers, and a Keto Mahi. Try our local moonshines from Yalaha Bootleggin Co in one of our #DrinkLocal cocktails.
